HEADWORD: Godlike
<hw>God"like`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[<ets>God</ets> +
<ets>like.</ets> Cf. <er>Godly</er>.]</ety> <def>Resembling or befitting
